ECHO ============================================================
ECHO TABLE BUFFER VISIBILITY / ROLLBACK / PERSISTENCE STUB TEST
ECHO ============================================================

DO x64

SCHEMAS OPEN DBF

SELECT STUDENTS
TOP

ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO BASELINE - committed physical/current visible value
ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
LIST 1
TUP

ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO RAM BUFFER OVERLAY TEST
ECHO Expected: LIST and SMARTLIST show ROLLTEST
ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
TABLE BUFFER ON
REPLACE LNAME WITH "ROLLTEST"
LIST 1
SMARTLIST 1
TUP

ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO ROLLBACK TEST
ECHO Expected: value returns to prior committed value
ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ROLLBACK
LIST 1
SMARTLIST 1
TUP

ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO PERSISTENCE STUB COMMAND TEST
ECHO Expected: commands accepted; no real journal behavior yet
ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
TABLE BUFFER ON PERSISTENT
TABLE BUFFER STATUS
TABLE BUFFER JOURNAL OFF
TABLE BUFFER STATUS
TABLE BUFFER JOURNAL ON
TABLE BUFFER STATUS
TABLE BUFFER ON RAM
TABLE BUFFER STATUS

ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO COMMIT TEST WITH TEMP VALUE
ECHO Expected: COMMIT writes COMMITTEST
ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
TABLE BUFFER ON
REPLACE LNAME WITH "COMMITTEST"
LIST 1
SMARTLIST 1
COMMIT
LIST 1
SMARTLIST 1
TUP

ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
ECHO RESTORE TEST VALUE BACK TO ZZZTEST
ECHO Expected: final committed value is ZZZTEST
ECHO ------------------------------------------------------------
TABLE BUFFER ON
REPLACE LNAME WITH "ZZZTEST"
COMMIT
LIST 1
SMARTLIST 1
TUP

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO END TABLE BUFFER TEST
ECHO ============================================================
